rows.label: tlk42100141_03_msg0001
rows.name:
Did you know Vandham-san used
to live in Fons Maim before
he became a mercenary?

rows.label: tlk42100141_03_msg0002
rows.name:
Of course, Vandham is just a
nickname. His real name is
Aquila Paronet Sol Esteriole.

rows.label: tlk42100141_03_msg0003
rows.name:
He's actually a scion of the
noble Paronet family of Invidia.

rows.label: tlk42100141_03_msg0004
rows.name:
Vandham's just a name that he
borrowed from a famous person
that he looked up to as a kid.

rows.label: tlk42100141_03_msg0005
rows.name:
I heard him mention that in his more
sprightly days. I'm very knowledgeable
when it comes to these things.
